#. <section class="sutta" id="sn8.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga"
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn8.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Nikkhantasutta"
msgstr "1. Renounced"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.185"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.398"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "sn8.1:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. </span>
msgctxt "sn8.1:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā vaṅgīso āḷaviyaṃ viharati aggāḷave cetiye āyasmatā "
"nigrodhakappena upajjhāyena saddhiṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Vaṅgīsa was staying near Āḷavī, at the Aggāḷava Tree-"
"shrine, together with his mentor, Venerable Nigrodhakappa."

msgctxt "sn8.1:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā vaṅgīso navako hoti acirapabbajito ohiyyako "
"vihārapālo."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time Vaṅgīsa was junior, recently gone forth. He had been left "
"behind to look after the dwelling."

msgctxt "sn8.1:1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā itthiyo samalaṅkaritvā yena aggāḷavako ārāmo "
"tenupasaṅkamiṃsu vihārapekkhikāyo."
msgstr ""
"Then several women dressed in all their finery went to the monastery at "
"Aggāḷava in order to inspect the dwelling."

msgctxt "sn8.1:1.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa tā itthiyo disvā anabhirati uppajjati, rāgo "
"cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti."
msgstr ""
"When Vaṅgīsa saw them he became dissatisfied, with lust infecting his mind."

msgctxt "sn8.1:1.6"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then he thought:"

msgctxt "sn8.1:1.7"
msgid ""
"“alābhā vata me, na vata me lābhā; dulladdhaṃ vata me, na vata me suladdhaṃ; "
msgstr "“It’s my loss, my misfortune, "

msgctxt "sn8.1:1.8"
msgid ""
"yassa me anabhirati uppannā, rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti, taṃ kutettha labbhā, "
"yaṃ me paro anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ uppādeyya."
msgstr ""
"that I’ve become dissatisfied, with lust infecting my mind. How is it "
"possible for someone else to dispel my discontent and give rise to "
"satisfaction?"

msgctxt "sn8.1:1.9"
msgid ""
"Yannūnāhaṃ attanāva attano anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ uppādeyyan”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I do it myself?”"

msgctxt "sn8.1:1.10"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso attanāva attano anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ "
"uppādetvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then, on the occasion of dispelling his own discontent and giving rise to "
"satisfaction, he recited these verses:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.1:2.1"
msgid "“Nikkhantaṃ vata maṃ santaṃ,"
msgstr "“Now that I’ve renounced"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:2.2"
msgid "agārasmānagāriyaṃ;"
msgstr "the home life for homelessness"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:2.3"
msgid "Vitakkā upadhāvanti,"
msgstr "I’m assailed"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:2.4"
msgid "pagabbhā kaṇhato ime."
msgstr "by the reckless thoughts of the Dark One."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.1:3.1"
msgid "Uggaputtā mahissāsā,"
msgstr "Even if a thousand mighty princes and great archers,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:3.2"
msgid "sikkhitā daḷhadhammino;"
msgstr "well trained, with strong bows,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:3.3"
msgid "Samantā parikireyyuṃ,"
msgstr "were to completely surround me;"

# https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/could-someone-with-a-copy-of-normans-elders-verses-help-me-out/3579/9
#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:3.4"
msgid "sahassaṃ apalāyinaṃ."
msgstr "I would never flee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: etato → ettato (bj, pts1-2, mr) | ettako (si) | ettakā (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn8.1:4.1"
msgid "Sacepi etato bhiyyo,"
msgstr "And even if women come,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:4.2"
msgid "āgamissanti itthiyo;"
msgstr "many more than that,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: byādhayissanti → byāthayissanti (?)
msgctxt "sn8.1:4.3"
msgid "Neva maṃ byādhayissanti,"
msgstr "they won’t scare me,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:4.4"
msgid "dhamme samhi patiṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "for I stand firm in the teaching."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.186"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.400"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.1:5.1"
msgid "Sakkhī hi me sutaṃ etaṃ,"
msgstr "I heard this with my own ears"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:5.2"
msgid "buddhassādiccabandhuno;"
msgstr "from the Buddha, Kinsman of the Sun,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:5.3"
msgid "Nibbānagamanaṃ maggaṃ,"
msgstr "about the path going to extinguishment;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:5.4"
msgid "tattha me nirato mano."
msgstr "that’s what delights my mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.1:6.1"
msgid "Evañce maṃ viharantaṃ,"
msgstr "Wicked One, if you come near me"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:6.2"
msgid "pāpima upagacchasi;"
msgstr "as I live like this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:6.3"
msgid "Tathā maccu karissāmi,"
msgstr "I’ll make sure that you, Death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.1:6.4"
msgid "na me maggampi dakkhasī”ti."
msgstr "won’t even see the path I travel.”"
